description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 9, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 9, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 2 for East, Leverage for South, and 5 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90091-82652-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [9 Votes, Common]
